precis:
Enactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON
TERRITORY (1999-No. 7, Tombstone Territorial Park Reservation, Y.T.) -
which (a) prohibits staking mineral claims or prospecting for precious
minerals on specified tracts of land in the Yukon, until December 31, 2004,
and (b) revokes Order in Council P.C. 1999-2226.
